h4. Actor:
Configuration Manager.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Settings|guide:_ShowApplicationPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Development" sub menu from left menu.
* Click "Mail" link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Mail"|guide:ShowAppMailActionService].
* Select a Line-Item from grid view.
* Click "Edit" button from tool bar.
* Open "Mail" in Edit Mode.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Select App Mail" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get "Mail" details from server.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show selected "Mail" information in input form.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].
